description: The London Fish and Chippy homemade beer batter is the perfect dip for preparing their specialty haddock fish and chips. This authentic beer batter is just not for fish but every thing they can dip in it; jumbo shrimp with coconut flakes, calamari, tentacles, and onion rings. Bringing seafood lover's a vast selection of fresh fried seafood you will enjoy. Be sure to watch out for the Gator Tail Taco special before it runs out!
name: The London Fish and Chippy
